    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "程妻",
        "程婴",
        "韩厥"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（程婴上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "程婴",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼望韩厥不得见，"
        },
        {
          "character": "程婴",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好叫我两眼都望穿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（韩厥上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩厥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩厥",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怀抱孤儿往前奔，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩厥",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见了程兄说分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程婴",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤儿可曾抱出宫来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩厥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抱出宫来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程婴",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘子在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（程妻上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "程妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "官人何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "程婴",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快抱了进去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（程妻下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩厥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "程兄，出宫之时，太后言道：须要用心抚养。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程婴",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那个自然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩厥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程婴",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军请转。此事只有你知我知，千万不可泄漏。请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩厥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（韩厥下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "程婴",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住，我想左邻右舍，谁人不知：我程婴只生一子。如今多了一个婴儿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "程婴",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘若有人出首，如何是好？哦，有了，我想公孙兄，乃是赵相门客，不免与他"
        },
        {
          "character": "程婴",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "商议商议。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "程婴",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要救孤儿命，须寻仗义人。"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "程婴→韩厥",
          "turns": 4
